Future - OSPFv3

OSPFv3 needed to support IPv6

Protocol enough different to need to write a new daemon

Some slow progress going on
first hello packets are moving

IPv6 is painful
needs normally about 5 times more code compared to IPv4

hopefully minimal support in OpenBSD 4.3

